reviews.name: Alias: The Complete Second Season (Widescreen)
reviews.reviewText: It has been a long time since I've seen Alias, but viewing Season 1 when I was sick made me want to see it all again. I've just viewed the entire Season 2 set in about 3 days and am going to be ordering the rest of the seasons ASAP. Love the bonus material. I am an Alias freak!
reviews.title: Most Enjoyable

reviews.name: Alias: The Complete Second Season (Widescreen)
reviews.reviewText: I picked up on "Alias" a few years into the story line when I found it in syndication. But I never understood many things. Having finished viewing Season I I was delighted to find Season II for such a reasonable price at Walmart. GREAT viewing!
reviews.title: The Second In a GREAT Series
